<br>
One with ancient bo, focus gloves, and the frenzied bo.  <br>
One with just Bo4.<br>
<br>
There is approx. 8 dps difference. (The sampling isn't really high enough yet for 100% accuracy but enough to give an an overview.)<br>
<br>
I think they are going to make certain spells to pump up the pets rather than make a new epic or make the epic stronger. (ie. like beastlords)  <br>
<br>
Look at the stats for ancient bo vs Bo4... 40 attack and Bunch of str difference. <br>
<br>
As far as the 61 to 65 pets being tougher, I dunno there is a huge gap already between the epic and the other pets.  I'd like to see an epic_v2 but I don't think we will.  I think the 65 pet will be equal to the epic in most cases, but greater.. doubtful.<br>
